vernac_cmds: Definition conseq : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (a : A) (v : seq n A), seq (S n) A.

apply (Build_Map (Ap:=fun m : fin (S n) => match m return (A:Type) with | Build_finiteT x0 x1 => match x0 as x2 return (x2 < S n -> (A:Type)) with | O => fun _ : 0 < S n => a | S m' => fun HSm' : S m' < S n => Ap v (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n m' n HSm')) end x1 end)).
Notation "a ;; b" := (conseq a b) (at level 60, right associativity).
Lemma cons_comp : forall (a' : A) (v v' : seq n A), a =' a' in _ -> v =' v' in _ -> a;; v =' a';; v' in _.
Lemma cons_first_element : forall (v : seq n A) (H : 0 < S n), (a;; v) (Build_finiteT H) =' a in _.
Definition head (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (v : seq (S n) A) := v (Build_finiteT (lt_O_Sn n)).
Lemma head_comp : forall (A : Setoid) (n : Nat) (v v' : seq (S n) A), v =' v' in _ -> head v =' head v' in _.
Lemma head_unfolding1 : forall v : seq (S n) A, v (Build_finiteT (lt_O_Sn n)) =' a in _ -> head v =' a in _.
Lemma head_unfolding2 : forall v : seq (S n) A, a =' v (Build_finiteT (lt_O_Sn n)) in _ -> a =' head v in _.
Hint Extern 0 (head _ =' _ in _) => unfold head in |- *: algebra.
Hint Extern 0 (_ =' head _ in _) => unfold head in |- *: algebra.
Lemma head_cons_inv : forall v : seq n A, head (a;; v) =' a in _.
Lemma seq_S_O_contains_single_elt : forall (A : Setoid) (v : seq 1 A) (i : fin 1), v i =' head v in _.
Lemma seq_S_O_head_fixes_everything : forall (A : Setoid) (v v' : seq 1 A), head v =' head v' in _ -> v =' v' in _.
apply Trans with (head v'); auto with algebra.
Lemma cons_later_elements : forall (v : seq n A) (i : Nat) (Hi : S i < S n) (Hi' : i < n), (a;; v) (Build_finiteT Hi) =' v (Build_finiteT Hi') in _.
Definition Seqtl : forall n : Nat, seq n A -> seq (pred n) A.
apply (Build_Map (Ap:=fun i' : fin m => match i' with | Build_finiteT i Hi => f (Build_finiteT (lt_n_S _ _ (Hi:i < m))) end)).
Lemma Seqtl_comp : forall v v' : seq n A, v =' v' in _ -> Seqtl v =' Seqtl v' in _.
Definition hdtl (v : seq (S n) A) := head v;; Seqtl v:seq (S n) A.
Lemma conseq_hdtl : forall (v : seq (S n) A) (H : 0 < S n), v =' v (Build_finiteT H);; Seqtl v in _.
intros; apply Ap_comp; simpl in |- *; auto with algebra arith.
intros; apply Ap_comp; simpl in |- *; auto with algebra arith.
Lemma hdtl_x_is_x : forall v : seq (S n) A, v =' hdtl v in _.
Hint Extern 0 (head _;; Seqtl _ =' _ in _) => fold hdtl in |- *; apply Sym; apply hdtl_x_is_x: algebra.
Hint Extern 0 (_ =' head _;; Seqtl _ in _) => fold hdtl in |- *; apply hdtl_x_is_x: algebra.
Lemma cons_lemma_nice : forall P : Predicate (seq (S n) A), (forall (a : A) (v : seq n A), Pred_fun P (a;; v)) -> forall w : seq (S n) A, Pred_fun P w.
apply Pred_compatible_prf with (hdtl w); auto with algebra.
Lemma cons_lemma_verynice : forall (P : Predicate (seq (S n) A)) (H : 0 < S n) (w : seq (S n) A), Pred_fun P (w (Build_finiteT H);; Seqtl w) -> Pred_fun P w.
apply Pred_compatible_prf with (w (Build_finiteT H);; Seqtl w); auto with algebra.
Lemma Seqtl_cons_inv : forall v : seq n A, Seqtl (a;; v) =' v in _.
Lemma Seqtl_to_seq : forall (v : seq (S n) A) (i : Nat) (Hi : i < n) (HSi : S i < S n), Seqtl v (Build_finiteT Hi) =' v (Build_finiteT HSi) in _.
Lemma split_hd_tl_equality : forall v w : seq (S n) A, head v =' head w in _ -> Seqtl v =' Seqtl w in _ -> v =' w in _.
apply Trans with (head v); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (head w); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (Seqtl v (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ in_range_prf))); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (Seqtl w (Build_finiteT (lt_S_n _ _ in_range_prf))); auto with algebra.
Notation "a ;; b" := (conseq a b) (at level 60, right associativity).
Hint Extern 0 (head _ =' _ in _) => unfold head in |- *: algebra.
Hint Extern 0 (_ =' head _ in _) => unfold head in |- *: algebra.
Hint Extern 0 (head _;; Seqtl _ =' _ in _) => fold hdtl in |- *; apply Sym; apply hdtl_x_is_x: algebra.
Hint Extern 0 (_ =' head _;; Seqtl _ in _) => fold hdtl in |- *; apply hdtl_x_is_x: algebra.
